						"title": "Isolate applications",
						"subtitle": null,
						"copy": "# Secure sensitive data by running application sessions in an isolated browser – now with just one click.\n\nCloudflare's ZTNA service, [Access](https://www.cloudflare.com/products/zero-trust/access/), verifies user access to applications against Zero Trust policies like identity and device posture. \n\nGoing forward, administrators will be able to turn on isolation policies for internal and SaaS applications with a single click. Running user sessions in an isolated browser allows administrators to apply controls that prevent the leak of sensitive data, including restricting copy/paste, downloads, and more.\n\nSign up now to join the beta and test out this new, streamlined workflow and simplify how your organization secures data.\n\n![Access + Browser Isolation + DLP for self-hosted apps](//cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/3woFduTB96A6EfYV0b9PAD/f8ca810605692cb35101f0b4e7ebc220/Access___Browser_Isolation___DLP_for_self-hosted_apps.png)",
